div.div: The report contains the list of photos grouped into 3 categories: photos in an unknown status, photos that failed to upload and photos successfully uploaded (in that order).
Photos with unknown status are photos that started to upload, but since the internet connection was lost, the app doesn't know their status.
If the user canceled the upload at any time, the photos that didn't start to upload are not listed.
